1
00:01:57,980 --> 00:02:00,100
1931,

2
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:05,500
5 Chinese merchant families in Siam were running their businesses successfully

3
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:08,500
they gathered up to form Five Dragons Association

4
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:13,500
and they became the most influential association in Siam, economically.

5
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:18,500
The absolute power and decision of the association

6
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:22,500
was in the palm of the leader's hand which was Song Family,

7
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:25,500
and he was elected by the members of five families.

8
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:31,500
The association leader position will be succeeded to the first son of Song Family.

9
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:37,500
If any heir of successor ruined association's reputation,

10
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:44,500
the members could fire that successor and elect the new heir.

11
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:49,500
Song Family Residence

12
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:54,500
5 Dragons' Meeting.

13
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:22,500
Bring them to the guests, carefully.

14
00:03:22,700 --> 00:03:25,500
It will be a key meeting of Five Dragons Association.

15
00:03:25,700 --> 00:03:27,500
Don't ruin it, you hear that?

16
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:29,500
Yes, ma'am.

17
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:36,500
Mom? Can I go out and play? It's so boring in here.

18
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:40,500
You have to stay here / Sure.

19
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,500
Where's my big brother?

20
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:49,500
He's praying to the gods. If everyone is here, I'll go get him.

21
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:53,500
I'm sorry for welcoming you late.

22
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:57,500
Say hi to mister and Xiaotong.

23
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:07,500
What are you talking about?

24
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:13,300
We're discussing about coffee that the association will import.

25
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:14,500
Who will take care of it?

26
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:21,500
Shun and I both agreed that Zhang should take care of it.

27
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:25,500
Well, congratulations is in order then.

28
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:28,500
Maybe it could be different from everyone's expectation.

29
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:36,500
Because our big brother hasn't assigned this task to anyone yet.

30
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,500
In my opinion,

31
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:44,500
I think I'm more suitable for this position than you.

32
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:56,500
Miss Chan?

33
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:03,500
Please continue talking, excuse me.

34
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:11,500
Bua! What the hell are you doing here?

35
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:16,500
You know that they're hosting a party and you're rushing here?

36
00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:21,500
You're just a mistress, you should know your place.

37
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:26,500
I'm about to head to the market, I need to use this path.

38
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,500
I didn't even know that they hosted a party up there.

39
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:32,500
You're going to the market? Can I come with?

40
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:36,500
I won't let you. Why did you want to go with her?

41
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:43,500
Fine. Then I'll go play somewhere else. / Stop it.

42
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:51,100
If there is nothing else, I need to be excused.

43
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:54,500
She said that she wanted to go to the market and used this path.

44
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:57,500
Actually, she wanted Mr.Song to see her.

45
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:02,500
So he would think of her and go to see her, right?

46
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:21,500
Yang!

47
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:33,500
Bring him to play somewhere else, don't let him be around here.

48
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:35,500
The adults are talking about something important.

49
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,500
Let's go, Tian.

50
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:40,500
Why can't my son and I get in?

51
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:43,500
When you and your son can get in.

52
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:47,500
My son and your son are different.

53
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:53,500
My son is the first son, he will be the successor of our husband

54
00:06:53,700 --> 00:06:56,500
and he will succeed the leader position in the association.

55
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:06,500
Your son is the second son, he is minor choice of this family.

56
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:33,500
Li, you scum dancer! I really hate her.

57
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,500
I hate her too. Actually, the female head of the house

58
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,500
should belong to you.

59
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:41,500
You're a daughter of aristocrat.

60
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:44,500
You're superior to her.

61
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:46,500
I was here a little later than her.

62
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:50,500
So I was the second place and she could push me to the ground.

63
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:56,500
Yang was born just one night after Tian.

64
00:07:56,600 --> 00:08:01,300
That's quite upsetting. If only he had been born just a little bit earlier,

65
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:05,500
he'd have been the first son and the successor of the family.

66
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,500
Just let it go, we can't change it.

67
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:12,500
The second wife like me and my son

68
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:16,500
will take everything from her and her son.

69
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:26,900
Take a look at all of them,

70
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:32,500
these people, they are significant people of the association.

71
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:39,500
That one is Mr.Sung. He's the owner of the biggest ferry business in Bangkok.

72
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:44,500
That one is Cai Xiaotong. She's the leader of Cai Family.

73
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:51,500
After her husband passed away, she is taking care of tea house business.

74
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:57,500
The last two people are Mr.Ma and Mr.Zhang.

75
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:01,500
Mr.Ma is operating rice mill business

76
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:06,500
and Mr.Zhang is taking care of agricultural products' import and export.

77
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:09,500
And distributing the products to various big provinces.

78
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:12,500
Everyone is gathering here today

79
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:16,500
to elect either Mr. Ma or Mr. Zhang, who will take care of coffee

80
00:09:16,700 --> 00:09:21,500
that the association will import.

81
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:30,500
Look at Tian. He is frowning. He doesn't understand any of this.

82
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:32,500
I need to tell him all of this.

83
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:39,500
You may not understand about this now but you need to learn about it.

84
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:43,500
Because you will be the leader of Song Family in the future.

85
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:47,500
And you will be the leader of Five Dragons Association after your father.

86
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:20,500
Mr.Song is coming.

87
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:27,500
The meeting is about to start. You should go outside and play.

88
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:30,500
And don't make any noises around here.

89
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:34,500
The adults will discuss something important. Understand?

90
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:17,500
I called all of you here today

91
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:23,500
to hear the decision of who will take care of coffee import business.

92
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:30,000
And I decided that the most suitable one is…

93
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,000
Zhang.

94
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:43,500
Why did you let Zhang to take care of it? I am the one contacting this.

95
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:49,500
This job requires someone who is careful and detail-oriented.

96
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:54,500
I made a decision and Zhang is the most suitable one for this job.

97
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:57,500
Please take care of this.

98
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:00,500
Thank you for trusting me.

99
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:04,500
Congrats.

100
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:20,500
It's alright. I knew that you would let Zhang to take care of it.

101
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:27,500
But I want you to make another decision.

102
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:31,500
About what?

103
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:38,500
Let me go / Get out

104
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:42,500
Let me go. I didn't do anything.

105
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:19,500
Poj? Ma,what did you do to my people?

106
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:27,500
Tell him what is your relationship with Poj?

107
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:31,500
What do you mean?

108
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,500
Hey!

109
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:54,500
Stop!

110
00:13:58,500 --> 00:13:59,500
Are you okay?

111
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:09,500
Tell him what is your relationship with Poj?

112
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:14,500
Speak! Tell him.

113
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:25,500
What is it?

114
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:33,500
Zhang is homosexual.

115
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:45,500
What is homosexual?

116
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:47,500
I don't know.

117
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:49,500
Homosexual?

118
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:51,500
What is it?

119
00:14:57,500 --> 00:14:58,500
Homosexual?

120
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:07,500
You like men?

121
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:11,500
How did you know that he is one?

122
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:22,500
This is a lover letter of Zhang and Poj, his lover.

123
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:41,500
Sir? Please don't mix this with business.

124
00:15:41,700 --> 00:15:45,500
I run the business successfully. I've never made any mistakes.

125
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:48,500
Don't judge me based on my personal preferences.

126
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:52,500
Why can't we? What if someone knew about this

127
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:55,500
what would people look at us?

128
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:59,500
You are the one ruining the association's reputation, you take advantage of people

129
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:04,500
You use your power to harass people. Don't you think I didn't know any of this.

130
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:10,500
You can talk whatever you want but where's the proof?

131
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:16,500
How can we let a homosexual run the business? There's only one way to fail.

132
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:19,500
Please bring me justice.

133
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:22,500
It's me who're asking for justice.

134
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:30,500
There's a homosexual in the association. Who would want to partner with us?

135
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:33,500
You ruined the reputation. This is humiliating.

136
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:35,800
Stop. That's enough.

137
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:45,500
Ma, you will take care of imported coffee business.

138
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:49,500
Thank you for the justice.

139
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:52,500
You are judging me like this?

140
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:58,500
I've dedicated everything for the members because we're family.

141
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:01,500
Just because I'm a homosexual

142
00:17:01,700 --> 00:17:06,500
and you let a gangster like Ma taking care of the business instead of me?

143
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:14,500
When the association opened Chinese opera house or sewing business, you can take care of that.

144
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:18,300
You should go home. We’ll talk later.

145
00:17:18,500 --> 00:17:20,500
I'm not going back. Let's talk here.

146
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:26,500
I've been working for Five Dragons Association my whole life.

147
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:33,500
Now I know that it was useless. I shouldn't have respected you.

148
00:17:34,500 --> 00:17:37,500
You're closed-minded and you're unfair.

149
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:45,500
You're a homosexual, you love men.

150
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:48,500
You have to work on something that is more suitable for you,

151
00:17:49,500 --> 00:17:51,500
not the business that required good image like this.

152
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:57,500
What if the outsiders knew about this, what would happen to the association?

153
00:17:58,500 --> 00:18:00,500
It's not just about you.

154
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:03,500
It's about our brothers and sisters here.

155
00:18:04,500 --> 00:18:06,500
In your opinion,

156
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:12,500
me being a homosexual is that disgusting?

157
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:20,500
Fine. When all of your hearts are all close-minded,

158
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:23,500
I won't be here anymore.

159
00:18:24,500 --> 00:18:30,500
If you're serious about this, you should remove Zhang Family out of the association.

160
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:37,500
Fine. Listen to me carefully.

161
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:46,500
From now on, Zhang Family won't be a part of Five Dragons Association.

162
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:51,500
We will take over all of your businesses.

163
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:54,500
Sir?

164
00:18:56,500 --> 00:18:58,500
I lost my respected siblings

165
00:19:00,500 --> 00:19:03,500
it doesn't matter if I have to lose my business either.

166
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:14,500
From now on, it will be only four families in the association,

167
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:18,500
and it is just a doomed association.

168
00:19:18,700 --> 00:19:24,500
Shut your mouth and go home.

169
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:27,500
Don't make me sadder than this.

170
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:32,500
Please, I beg you.

171
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:37,500
Don't judge him like this. I beg you.

172
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:39,500
Let go of his hand.
Please don't judge him like this

173
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:40,500
I told you to let go of his hand.

174
00:19:42,500 --> 00:19:43,500
That's enough.

175
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,500
Let's go home.

176
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:18,500
Tian and Yang, come here.

177
00:20:19,500 --> 00:20:23,500
What're you looking at? Stop it, come here.

178
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:29,500
Stay here, please.

179
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:32,500
Why did they have to hurt that man?

180
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:34,500
I don't know either.

181
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:38,100
Maybe he did something really bad.

182
00:20:38,300 --> 00:20:42,500
Tian and I heard that the abused man is a homosexual.

183
00:20:42,600 --> 00:20:44,500
What is a homosexual?

184
00:20:46,500 --> 00:20:48,800
I…I don't know either.

185
00:20:49,100 --> 00:20:52,500
Why don't you ask someone who knew more about this?

186
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:57,500
I think we should get out of here.

187
00:20:58,500 --> 00:20:59,300
Come on,

188
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:02,500
That's Pao. He should know about this. Let's ask him.

189
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:06,500
Wait! Tian! Yang!

190
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:10,500
What is a homosexual?

191
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:12,500
Where did you hear it from?

192
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:16,500
Did you play where the adults were discussing?

193
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:19,500
So what does it mean?

194
00:21:21,500 --> 00:21:24,500
The Mandarin word of this literal translated as "the passion of the cut sleeve"

195
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:28,500
It was started from the old days.

196
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:31,500
Emperor Ai of Han

197
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:36,500
was a handsome emperor but he never cared for any women.

198
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:41,500
But he fell in love with a man named Dong Xian

199
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:43,500
he's a royal page in a palace.

200
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:47,500
And he had to pretend to be eunuch so he could work closely to the emperor.

201
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:50,500
They were passionately in love

202
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:54,500
One day, after falling asleep for a nap on the same bed, Emperor Ai 

203
00:21:55,500 --> 00:22:00,500
saw his lover was still asleep on his sleeve.

204
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:07,500
So he cut off his sleeve rather than disturb the sleeping Dong Xian

205
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:11,500
when he had to get out of bed. So his lover could sleep comfortably.

206
00:22:11,700 --> 00:22:17,500
People use this word to refer to a man who loves another man.

207
00:22:18,500 --> 00:22:21,500
Or we called them gay.

208
00:22:22,100 --> 00:22:24,100
I don't understand any of this / Right.

209
00:22:24,500 --> 00:22:29,500
You don't have to. Homosexual is taboo. It is forbidden and it's not good.

210
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:34,500
If they want someone to accept that, no one would be sympathized.

211
00:22:34,700 --> 00:22:36,500
And no one would feel empathy for them.

212
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:39,500
Why do they need anyone to feel empathy for them?

213
00:22:40,500 --> 00:22:45,500
It's about two people who have the same feeling, regardless of gender.

214
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:50,500
They should be able to choose happiness in their lives, shouldn't they?

215
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:10,500
About Zhang, I think…

216
00:23:15,500 --> 00:23:18,500
You think I was too harsh on him?

217
00:23:21,500 --> 00:23:26,500
I didn't say that you were too harsh but this is sensitive.

218
00:23:27,500 --> 00:23:33,500
You should think it through. You're brothers. I feel bad for him.

219
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:38,500
Do you think that I don't feel bad for him?

220
00:23:38,900 --> 00:23:45,500
Among all the members in the association, I love him and adore him the most and you know that.

221
00:23:46,500 --> 00:23:52,500
This is not personal. If I was too soft on him and acting like nothing happened,

222
00:23:55,500 --> 00:23:57,500
Ma could call me out.

223
00:23:59,500 --> 00:24:05,500
And what Ma said was right. What if the outsiders knew about this,

224
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:10,500
the businesses in the association would be shaken.

225
00:24:11,500 --> 00:24:13,500
Everyone will be in trouble.

226
00:24:15,500 --> 00:24:20,500
I agreed to cut him off because of everyone.

227
00:24:23,500 --> 00:24:28,500
What about this? When everything is cooling down,

228
00:24:29,500 --> 00:24:30,500
and everyone is calming down…

229
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:33,500
Sir? Something bad happened.

230
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:48,500
Zhang? Why did you come back?

231
00:25:04,500 --> 00:25:08,500
You gave me this money when we arrived in Siam,

232
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:16,500
we swore to be brothers, to help one another and to start business together.

233
00:25:17,500 --> 00:25:22,500
Now I gave it all back to you. We're done.

234
00:25:27,500 --> 00:25:30,500
Don't disappoint me than I already am.

235
00:25:31,500 --> 00:25:33,500
I disappointed in you too.

236
00:25:34,500 --> 00:25:39,500
It was hurt that Ma called me out but it was nothing compared to being banished by you.

237
00:25:40,500 --> 00:25:44,500
You judged me like we used to be in tough time together.

238
00:25:45,500 --> 00:25:51,500
I shouldn't have love and looked up to you. I see you as my own father.

239
00:25:57,500 --> 00:26:00,500
If you see me as your father,

240
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:04,500
you need to understand me.

241
00:26:05,500 --> 00:26:12,500
You know how much we struggled to develop

242
00:26:13,500 --> 00:26:15,500
the association to become this successful.

243
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:23,500
If anyone knew that you're a homosexual, everyone's business will be ruined.

244
00:26:24,500 --> 00:26:26,500
It's not just about you.

245
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:33,500
I know that I'm a homosexual.

246
00:26:37,500 --> 00:26:39,500
But you're my brother,

247
00:26:42,500 --> 00:26:46,500
you acted like I'm someone else just because I'm not a real man.

248
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:54,500
No matter how much you tried to say.

249
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:59,500
I can't take back my own decision.

250
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:01,500
I'm not here to persuade you to change your mind.

251
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:08,500
I know. No matter how well I'm trying.

252
00:27:10,500 --> 00:27:14,500
I can't be greater than the real man like you or Ma.

253
00:27:16,500 --> 00:27:18,500
But I want you to remember this.

254
00:27:21,500 --> 00:27:23,500
Even though I'm a homosexual,

