410
00:45:26,626 --> 00:45:27,326
Tian!

411
00:45:28,026 --> 00:45:29,026
Tian!

412
00:45:29,126 --> 00:45:30,026
Tian! / Tian!

413
00:45:33,026 --> 00:45:34,026
Jia!

414
00:45:34,226 --> 00:45:36,026
Tian!

415
00:45:36,126 --> 00:45:37,026
Tian!

416
00:45:38,026 --> 00:45:39,026
Tian!

417
00:45:40,026 --> 00:45:43,026
