00:55:43,026 --> 00:55:46,026
But you know who did this?

516
00:55:49,026 --> 00:55:51,026
I have something to ask you.

517
00:55:53,026 --> 00:55:58,026
Tian and Yang are so close

518
00:55:58,226 --> 00:56:00,026
they stay together since they were so young.

519
00:56:01,026 --> 00:56:03,026
I don't want their mothers' conflict

520
00:56:04,026 --> 00:56:07,026
to get in the way of siblings' love.

521
00:56:08,026 --> 00:56:10,026
I understand what you're trying to say.

522
00:56:12,026 --> 00:56:14,026
I don't want to hate Yang.

523
00:56:15,026 --> 00:56:21,026
But the bonding of mother and son is much stronger than sibling's bond.

524
00:56:23,026 --> 00:56:27,026
I don't know what Chan taught Yang.

525
00:56:29,026 --> 00:56:33,026
But I hope that when time passed

526
00:56:34,026 --> 00:56:39,026
Tian and Yang would continue to be loving siblings like this.

527
00:56:54,026 --> 00:56:58,026
Your wound is drying. You'll be able to walk soon.

528
00:57:08,026 --> 00:57:12,026
Yang? Come on in.

529
00:57:17,026 --> 00:57:19,026
You're here to play with Tian?

530
00:57:19,226 --> 00:57:24,026
That's right. I want to draw with Tian. His leg hurt and he can't go out to play.

531
00:57:25,026 --> 00:57:27,026
Please take care of him.

532
00:57:28,026 --> 00:57:33,026
Sure. Tian, let's draw.

533
00:57:41,026 --> 00:57:42,026
Let's go.

534
00:57:43,026 --> 00:57:44,026
But…

535
00:57:55,026 --> 00:57:57,926
Why did you let Tian with Yang?

536
00:57:58,026 --> 00:58:00,326
You know that Chan hates Tian so much.

537
00:58:00,426 --> 00:58:04,026
She could teach her son to hate Tian and hurt him too.

538
00:58:04,226 --> 00:58:08,026
You should have split both of them to be more distant.

539
00:58:08,626 --> 00:58:11,026
It's enough for me to fight with Chan.

540
00:58:12,026 --> 00:58:14,026
Yang is Chan's son

541
00:58:14,226 --> 00:58:19,026
but he shares the same blood as Tian. Their bond won't break.

542
00:58:22,026 --> 00:58:27,026
It'd be better for them to love each other than hate each other, don't you think?

543
00:58:43,626 --> 00:58:45,026
It's all done.

544
00:58:45,126 --> 00:58:46,626
Thank you.

545
00:58:51,026 --> 00:58:53,026
Be careful!

546
00:58:56,026 --> 00:59:00,026
Please wait for me, I'll get one for you.

547
00:59:04,026 --> 00:59:07,926
You haven't been here for days. How's your wound?

548
00:59:08,026 --> 00:59:09,026
It's getting better.

549
00:59:14,026 --> 00:59:17,026
What's going on?

550
00:59:19,026 --> 00:59:22,026
I don't want a sword. Can I get something else?

551
00:59:23,026 --> 00:59:25,026
What do you want?

552
00:59:25,226 --> 00:59:27,026
Can you get me a hairpin?

553
00:59:28,026 --> 00:59:30,026
A hairpin? / Yes.

554
00:59:47,026 --> 00:59:51,026
It's all done. Do you like it.

555
00:59:51,426 --> 00:59:55,026
I like it. It's so pretty.

556
01:00:34,626 --> 01:00:37,026
Tian, I brought you some snacks.

557
01:01:01,026 --> 01:01:02,026
Tian!

558
01:01:06,026 --> 01:01:07,026
Tian!

559
01:01:10,026 --> 01:01:11,026
What did you do?

560
01:01:13,026 --> 01:01:15,026
Why did you wrap your head with scarf like this?

561
01:01:18,026 --> 01:01:19,026
Where did you get it?

562
01:01:20,026 --> 01:01:23,026
Bua made it for me. She made this beautiful thing for me.

563
01:01:29,026 --> 01:01:34,026
This is bad. Tian starts to be like Mr.Zhang.

564
01:01:48,026 --> 01:01:58,026
Tell me, how often do you act like this? Has anyone seen you like this?

565
01:02:02,026 --> 01:02:04,026
Tian? / Ouch!

566
01:02:04,326 --> 01:02:10,026
Listen to me. You can't do this again. You hear me?

567
01:02:10,126 --> 01:02:11,026
Ouch!

568
01:02:11,326 --> 01:02:17,026
Listen to me. What you did was forbidden in this house.

569
01:02:17,226 --> 01:02:21,026
If you continue to be like this, you will have nothing.

570
01:02:21,326 --> 01:02:25,026
What you have will be taken from you.

571
01:02:26,026 --> 01:02:31,026
I forbid you to not do this again. You hear me?

572
01:02:59,026 --> 01:03:01,026
I'm here.

573
01:03:11,026 --> 01:03:12,026
Ms. Chan.

574
01:03:25,026 --> 01:03:26,026
Don't.

575
01:03:28,026 --> 01:03:33,026
Don't cry. Burn it.

576
01:03:35,026 --> 01:03:39,026
It's mine.

577
01:03:42,026 --> 01:03:44,026
What did she do?

578
01:03:45,026 --> 01:03:46,826
Don't / Tian!

579
01:03:47,026 --> 01:03:48,026
Don't / Stop!

580
01:03:49,026 --> 01:03:55,026
Listen to me. You can't let anyone know this secret. You hear me?

581
01:03:55,326 --> 01:04:00,026
If someone knew about this, you would be in trouble for sure. You hear me?

582
01:04:20,026 --> 01:04:21,026
Ms.Chan?

583
01:04:22,026 --> 01:04:23,026
Come on, it's about to burn all of this.

584
01:04:24,026 --> 01:04:25,026
Come on.

585
01:04:27,026 --> 01:04:29,026
So hot. / Hurry up.

586
01:04:31,026 --> 01:04:32,026
I got it.

587
01:04:32,126 --> 01:04:33,626
What the hell?

588
01:04:34,026 --> 01:04:36,026
They said it was a secret.

589
01:04:36,126 --> 01:04:37,026
A secret?

590
01:04:39,026 --> 01:04:40,826
A fabric and a stick?

591
01:04:41,026 --> 01:04:45,026
They said if anyone knew about Tian's secret, it would be a big trouble.

592
01:04:45,126 --> 01:04:47,026
Tian's secret?

593
01:04:52,026 --> 01:04:55,826
It must be something important and wicked.

594
01:04:56,026 --> 01:05:00,026
Otherwise, Madame and that old hag wouldn't be too serious about this.

595
01:05:03,026 --> 01:05:05,026
I need to know about this secret.

596
01:05:23,026 --> 01:05:24,026
Tian?

597
01:05:25,026 --> 01:05:30,026
I heard you said that the old one was ruined, so I brought you the new one.

598
01:05:33,026 --> 01:05:38,026
Why did you look like that? This one is not as pretty as the old one?

599
01:05:39,026 --> 01:05:41,626
It's pretty. But I can't play with it.

600
01:05:46,026 --> 01:05:48,026
What happened?

601
01:05:55,026 --> 01:05:59,026
It's okay if you don't want it.

602
01:05:59,126 --> 01:06:01,026
I'll get you something to eat.

603
01:06:33,026 --> 01:06:35,026
Where are you rushing to?

604
01:06:36,026 --> 01:06:38,026
I'm going back to my room.

605
01:06:38,326 --> 01:06:45,026
Don't go. Let's talk, what did you and your mom burn last night?

606
01:06:47,026 --> 01:06:50,026
I saw you cried.

607
01:06:51,026 --> 01:06:53,026
Did your mom force you to do something?

608
01:06:54,026 --> 01:06:57,026
You can tell me so I can help you.

609
01:07:02,026 --> 01:07:07,026
Tian hides something behind his back.

610
01:07:09,026 --> 01:07:14,026
What is that? Can I see? Let me see.

611
01:07:15,026 --> 01:07:17,026
Nope / Come on, let me see it.

612
01:07:17,126 --> 01:07:19,026
Nope / Nuan, help me.

613
01:07:19,226 --> 01:07:22,726
Please let me see that.

614
01:07:22,826 --> 01:07:23,826
Nope / Let me see it.

615
01:07:23,926 --> 01:07:25,026
Nope / Let me see.

616
01:07:25,226 --> 01:07:27,026
Show it to me.

617
01:07:27,126 --> 01:07:30,026
Nope.

618
01:07:30,126 --> 01:07:32,026
Please give it to me.

619
01:07:36,026 --> 01:07:38,026
How dare you hurting him!

620
01:07:41,026 --> 01:07:44,026
How dare your people hurt mine?

621
01:07:48,026 --> 01:07:49,026
What did you do?

622
01:08:04,026 --> 01:08:06,026
I didn't do anything.

623
01:08:06,326 --> 01:08:09,026
I saw he walked so I just came to say hi.

624
01:08:10,026 --> 01:08:16,026
But he acted weird so I came to talk to him.

625
01:08:16,126 --> 01:08:21,026
He was fighting me and then she came in.

626
01:08:21,126 --> 01:08:25,026
You liar! Normally, you didn't even want to look at my son's face.

627
01:08:25,126 --> 01:08:27,026
Why would you want to play with him now?

628
01:08:27,126 --> 01:08:32,026
My son was bitten by a snake and every car got flattened tires.

629
01:08:32,126 --> 01:08:36,026
I questioned you but I couldn't do anything because I had no proof.

630
01:08:36,326 --> 01:08:40,026
Today, I saw with my own eyes that you hurt my son.

631
01:08:42,026 --> 01:08:46,026
I confirmed that I didn't do anything to him,

632
01:08:46,126 --> 01:08:49,026
including the snake, the car or what happened today.

633
01:08:50,026 --> 01:08:52,026
If he hadn't act weirdly,

634
01:08:53,026 --> 01:08:55,026
I wouldn't have questioned about him and got involved.

635
01:08:57,026 --> 01:09:00,026
Or something happened?

636
01:09:01,026 --> 01:09:04,026
Does he have a secret to hide?

637
01:09:07,026 --> 01:09:13,026
That's enough. And you, don't mess with Tian anymore.

638
01:09:14,026 --> 01:09:17,026
You can just raise your son to be a good man and that should be enough.

639
01:09:19,026 --> 01:09:21,026
You hear me?

640
01:09:24,026 --> 01:09:25,026
Yes, sir.

641
01:09:39,026 --> 01:09:44,026
I told you not to play with this. Why didn't you listen to me?

642
01:09:45,026 --> 01:09:48,026
Please don't scold him. He was scared.

643
01:09:48,126 --> 01:09:51,026
If he was scared, he wouldn't have done something like that.

644
01:09:55,026 --> 01:09:59,026
Get up. I told you to get up.

645
01:10:02,026 --> 01:10:04,026
Get up. Now!

646
01:10:07,026 --> 01:10:12,026
When I forbid you and you didn't listen to me, then it'd be a punishment, you hear me?

647
01:10:15,026 --> 01:10:18,026
Fold your arms over your chest and turn around.

648
01:10:24,026 --> 01:10:25,026
Madame? Why were you here all of a sudden?

649
01:10:32,026 --> 01:10:34,026
Don't do that again.

650
01:10:35,026 --> 01:10:39,026
Didn't I tell you that if someone knew about this, you'd be in trouble?

651
01:10:40,026 --> 01:10:48,826
Remember! You have to listen to me.

652
01:10:49,026 --> 01:10:52,326
Remember that!
Please stop, please.

653
01:10:52,426 --> 01:10:58,026
He could be dead. Please, stop.

654
01:11:17,026 --> 01:11:23,026
12 years later.

655
01:11:41,026 --> 01:11:42,026
Tian!

656
01:11:43,326 --> 01:11:44,326
Tian!

657
01:11:47,026 --> 01:11:48,026
Tian!

658
01:12:42,026 --> 01:12:48,026
In memory of Tangmo Pattaratida (Nida) Patcharaveerapong.

659
01:12:56,026 --> 01:12:57,026
Damn it.

660
01:12:57,626 --> 01:12:59,026
Please bring me justice.

661
01:13:02,626 --> 01:13:04,026
Who're you?

662
01:13:05,026 --> 01:13:08,026
You've been working so hard and you should get some rest already.

663
01:13:08,126 --> 01:13:09,826
I want to rest too.

664
01:13:09,926 --> 01:13:14,026
According to the custom, Tian needs to get married and have children to continue the family.

665
01:13:20,026 --> 01:13:24,026
I need to know the truth before Tian accepts the position.
